data.description: This Bay Ridge Beauty is 100% MOVE IN READY! Open concept, single story, 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home can be your peaceful retreat or the perfect environment in which to entertain friends & loved ones!  Upgrades galore! Crown molding, trim details, tiled showers/tubs, sprinkler system, decked attic, stained cabinets, tile flooring throughout (excluding bedrooms). The grand entrance includes a dedicated foyer and extra storage. The spacious primary ensuite has dramatic tray ceilings & an abundance of windows for a terrific view of the backyard. The primary bathroom includes a soaking tub, a walk-in shower, plus a spacious walk-in closet & double vanity! Private junior ensuite is located just off the kitchen. The other 3 bedrooms are privately located near the front of the home - an ideal split bedroom design! The exterior features include an extended covered patio, outdoor fireplace and storage shed/workshop on a permitted, elevated concrete slab. Don’t miss out on this pristine home!
